data.description: Welcome yourself into this pristine 4bed/2bath home in the highly sought after Avery Park subdivision of New Braunfels, and make it yours today! This former DR Horton model home boasts the bright limestone exterior, brilliant tile and hard wood flooring, along with natural light, granite counters, walk-in pantry AND shower, and all as a desired corner lot. Covered front porch and back patio gives the welcoming feel for entertaining, with the options of a short walk to the soccer field, pool and playground. These motivated sellers have done a fresh coat of paint, as well as providing a lifetime transferable foundation warranty, New AC with warranty, New roof with warranty, new fence and new insulated garage door, all for an immediate move in! Sellers willing to contribute to a buyer's Interest Rate Buydown!
